Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.storemigration

Class SpatialConfigExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.storemigration.SpatialConfigExtractor
  • final class SpatialConfigExtractor
extends Object
    This class is the amber in which 3.5 spatial index provider is preserved in. Specifically it makes it possible to extract index configuration from an existing directory that contains the old spatial index provider directory structure with one index file for each coordinate reference system.
